{"phase": "description", "counterbalance": 2, "vidpath": "/static/video/I/filmfest_clip2_I_5.mp4", "descstop": 3, "vidpair": 6, "offset": "300", "content": "Frank told the FBI agent to help him but he replied that he would not fall for any of his tricks again. A few minutes later, Frank collapsed and the agent signalled for help from the prison warders to call a doctor. The prison warders rushed over and carried Frank to the infirmary. They placed him on a bed and stepped outside to wash their hands. The FBI agent asked when the doctor would be arriving and they said till the following day. The agent thought that was ridiculous that Frank would not be seen by a doctor immediately, and he started to threaten the prison warders. Shortly, there was a sound from Franks bed and one of the warders rushed to check. They all found an empty bed and the back door was left ajar as if someone had just escaped. Then they showed many prisoners making a lot of noise from their cells.", "importance": "6", "time": 437377, "tag": "test_seg6_desc"}
